  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad ir tu neſs tawu\nRaunu/ kas tu tawas Mahfas\nwiꞥnu bija/ tevi wiſſapfahrt\ndſinne.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr eß atgreesiſchu\nwiꞥao Zeetumu/ to Zeetumu\nSodomas un wiꞥnas Metto/\nin to Zeetumu Samartjas un\nwiꞥnas Meito/ un tohs Zeetum-\nneekus tawa Zeetuma wiꞥno\nWiddu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 54,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ka teiw buhß ta-\nwu Raunu nest/ un Raunā tapt/\nahr to wiſſu/ ko tu eſt darrijuſi/\nad tu wiꞥau eepeeziuaſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 55,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tawas Mahfas So-\ndoma un wiꞥnas Mettas atgree-\niſees pee fawas wezzas Buh-\nchaanas/ un Samartja ar fa-\nvalyn Meitahm atgreesiſees pee\nawas wezzas Buhſchaanas/ tad\ne tu ar tawahm Mettahm at-\ngreesiſees pee tawas wezzas\nBuhſchaanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 56,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jepthu tu tawas Mah-\nas Sodomas ar tawas Muttes\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 57,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Virms tawa Blehdiba\ntappe atklahta/ itt ka tanni Lat-\nek/ kad tahs Meitas no Silri-\njas tewi puſqoja/ un wiﬀas Met-\ntas to Wilistern/ kas apkahrt\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 58,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tew bij tawas Bleh-\nras un Negantibas janefs/ tak-\nka tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 59,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nKUNGS: Es darrischu tew\narridsan ka tu eſt darrijuſi/ kaß\ntu to Swehreſchann eſt nizzi-\nnajſi/ nn to Derribu pahrlausi-\njuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 60,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr eß atmiinneschu\nmannu Derribu ar tewim tawas\nJaunibas Deenas/ un uſzelkhu\nar tewim weenu muhschign Der-\nribu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 61,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atminneſi tu tawas\nZeetus/ un kauneſees/ kad tu ta-\nwas leelas un masas Mahfas\nuſkemſi/ jo es dohſchu tew tahs\npar Meitahm/bet ne tawas Der-\nribas pehz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 62,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo eß apſtiprinaſchu fa-\nwu Derribu ar tewtin/ un tu\nfajuttisi/ ka eß tas KUNGS\nejmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 63,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tew to buhß peemin-\nneht un kaunetees/ un tawa\nMutte wairs ne leelijahs tawa\nRauna deht/ kad es Salihdsina-\nschanu vreeſch tewtin darrischu/\npar wiſſu/ ko tu eſt darrijuſi/ fat-\nka tas KUNGS KUNGS.\n"
    }
  ],
